headline: Mizuho Raises DuPont (DD) Price Target, Cites Strong EV Supply Chain Role
summary: DuPont de Nemours, Inc. (NYSE:DD) is one of the best electric vehicle supply chain stocks to buy right now. On September 2, Mizuho reiterated the Outperform rating for DuPont de Nemours, Inc. (NYSE:DD), while increasing the 12-month price target from $85 to $90. That implies a 15.63% upside from the price of $77.82 as of September 5. […]
